## Assertion Cheat Sheet

### Boolean & Null

```php
$this->assertTrue($result);
$this->assertFalse($result);
$this->assertNull($result);
$this->assertNotNull($result);
```

### Type Checking

```php
$this->assertIsArray($result);
$this->assertIsString($result);
$this->assertIsInt($result);
$this->assertIsFloat($result);
$this->assertIsObject($result);
$this->assertIsCallable($result);
```

### Value Comparison

```php
$this->assertEquals($expected, $actual);           // ==
$this->assertNotEquals($expected, $actual);
$this->assertSame($expected, $actual);             // ===
$this->assertNotSame($expected, $actual);

$this->assertGreaterThan($threshold, $value);
$this->assertLessThan($threshold, $value);
$this->assertGreaterThanOrEqual($threshold, $value);
$this->assertLessThanOrEqual($threshold, $value);
```

### Collections

```php
$this->assertCount($expected, $array);
$this->assertEmpty($array);
$this->assertNotEmpty($array);
$this->assertContains('value', $array);
$this->assertNotContains('value', $array);
$this->assertArrayHasKey('key', $array);
$this->assertArrayNotHasKey('key', $array);
```

### Strings

```php
$this->assertStringContains('substr', $string);
$this->assertStringNotContains('substr', $string);
$this->assertStringStartsWith('prefix', $string);
$this->assertStringEndsWith('suffix', $string);
```

### Exception Testing (in ARRANGE)

```php
$this->expectException(MyException::class);
$this->expectExceptionMessage('Expected message');
$this->expectExceptionCode(123);
```

