## Common Commands

```bash
# Run all tests
./vendor/bin/phpunit

# Run specific test file
./vendor/bin/phpunit tests/Usecases/MyUsecaseTest.php

# Run specific test method
./vendor/bin/phpunit --filter testMethodName tests/Usecases/MyUsecaseTest.php

