## Debugging Tips

```php
// Print debug info (careful in tests!)
var_dump($variable);
echo json_encode($data, JSON_PRETTY_PRINT);

// Mock a method but let other calls through
$this->service->makePartial()
    ->shouldReceive('method')
    ->andReturn($value);

// Verify mock was called
// (Mockery throws error if expectations not met automatically)

// Check what was called
$this->repo->shouldHaveReceived('method')->times(2);

// Spy on actual calls
Mockery::spy(ServiceClass::class);
```

