## Remember

1. ✅ **Test ONE thing per test method**
2. ✅ **Use AAA Pattern** (Arrange, Act, Assert)
3. ✅ **Setup mocks with explicit expectations** (once, twice, etc.)
4. ✅ **Use descriptive test names**
5. ✅ **Mock external dependencies**
6. ✅ **Run tests frequently** during development
7. ✅ **Keep tests maintainable** - refactor test code like production code
8. ✅ **Test edge cases** - success, failures, exceptions, boundary conditions

